      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 21:20:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>将耗油大汽车换成电动车是否具有经济意义？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ev-costs-are-rising-are-they-better-value-than-gas-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[直到最近，购买电动汽车对于世界各地的许多人来说都是有意义的，不仅仅是出于环境原因，而且还有经济原因。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/ev-costs-are-rising-are-they-better-value-than-gas-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 20:38:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>超级富豪以外的所有人的房地产市场都崩溃了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/real-estate-market-is-broken-for-everyone-except-the-ultra-rich</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国是几十年来最难负担的房地产市场之一，住宅销售陷入停滞，一代有志于购房的人被拒之门外。但有一个群体却对这场危机泰然处之：富人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/real-estate-market-is-broken-for-everyone-except-the-ultra-rich</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 14:32:31 GMT</pubDate>
